chart.name: HTTP Response Count by Code
chart.programText:
D = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '5*')).sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='D')
B = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '3*')).sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='B')
C = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '4*')).sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='C')
A = data('http/server/response_count', filter=filter('response_code', '2*')).sum(by=['project_id']).publish(label='A')
